<p>Heyas, <br /> <br />I've been trying to find the sure-fire way to recharge my Staff of Forbidden Rites. I have heard theres a quest in PoK that allows you to recharge it. If ANYONE have ANY info in accordance to this quest or any other quest for recharging this item, PLEASE post your answer(s) here. <br /> <br />Thanks, <br /> <br />Nynelives (70 Rogue on Mith Marr)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>
